{"name":"t:sections.footer.name","type":"footer","sections":{"sp_custom_html_bEfNBj":{"type":"sp-custom-html","disabled":true,"name":"🚀SP - Custom HTML","settings":{"title":"","custom_html":"<div class=\"faq-section\">\n  <div class=\"faq-container\">\n\n    <span class=\"faq-label\">Support client<\/span>\n    <h2 class=\"faq-title\">Questions Fréquentes<\/h2>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-list\">\n\n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\" type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n          <span>Comment fonctionne la litière automatique ?<\/span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon-wrap\">\n            <svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 9L12 15L18 9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><\/path><\/svg>\n          <\/span>\n        <\/button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <div class=\"faq-answer-content\">\n            <p>La litière détecte automatiquement lorsque votre chat l'utilise. Après un délai de sécurité, elle nettoie les déchets et les stocke dans un compartiment fermé. Le processus est silencieux et hygiénique.<\/p>\n          <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\" type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n          <span>À quelle fréquence dois-je vider le bac à déchets ?<\/span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon-wrap\">\n            <svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 9L12 15L18 9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><\/path><\/svg>\n          <\/span>\n        <\/button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <div class=\"faq-answer-content\">\n            <p>Pour un chat, environ une fois par semaine. Pour plusieurs chats, tous les 3-4 jours. L'application vous envoie une notification lorsque le bac est presque plein.<\/p>\n          <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\" type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n          <span>Quel type de litière dois-je utiliser ?<\/span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon-wrap\">\n            <svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 9L12 15L18 9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><\/path><\/svg>\n          <\/span>\n        <\/button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <div class=\"faq-answer-content\">\n            <p>Nous recommandons la litière agglomérante sans parfum. Évitez les litières en cristaux ou en gel qui pourraient endommager le mécanisme. Versez jusqu'à la ligne de remplissage indiquée.<\/p>\n          <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\" type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n          <span>La litière est-elle bruyante ?<\/span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon-wrap\">\n            <svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 9L12 15L18 9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><\/path><\/svg>\n          <\/span>\n        <\/button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <div class=\"faq-answer-content\">\n            <p>Non, elle est conçue pour être ultra-silencieuse — moins de 45 dB.<\/p>\n          <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <button class=\"faq-question\" type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n          <span>Livrez-vous partout en France ?<\/span>\n          <span class=\"faq-icon-wrap\">\n            <svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 9L12 15L18 9\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><\/path><\/svg>\n          <\/span>\n        <\/button>\n        <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n          <div class=\"faq-answer-content\">\n            <p>Oui, toute la France métropolitaine et la Corse. Livraison gratuite en 6-12 jours ouvrés.<\/p>\n          <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<style>\n.faq-section {\n  padding: 80px 20px;\n  background: #ffffff;\n}\n\n.faq-container {\n  max-width: 780px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n  text-align: center;\n}\n\n.faq-label {\n  display: inline-block;\n  font-size: 11px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  letter-spacing: 0.12em;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  color: #B88B59;\n  background: #F3E8D8;\n  border: 1px solid #E8D5BC;\n  padding: 4px 12px;\n  border-radius: 20px;\n  margin-bottom: 14px;\n}\n\n.faq-title {\n  font-size: 32px;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  color: #1A1A18;\n  margin-bottom: 40px;\n  line-height: 1.2;\n}\n\n.faq-title::after {\n  content: '';\n  display: block;\n  width: 40px;\n  height: 3px;\n  background: #B88B59;\n  border-radius: 2px;\n  margin: 12px auto 0;\n}\n\n.faq-list {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  gap: 10px;\n  text-align: left;\n}\n\n.faq-item {\n  background: #FDF8F3;\n  border: 1px solid #E8D5BC;\n  border-radius: 12px;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  transition: box-shadow 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;\n}\n\n.faq-item:hover {\n  border-color: #B88B59;\n  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(184,139,89,0.1);\n}\n\n.faq-item.active {\n  background: #ffffff;\n  border-color: #B88B59;\n  box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(184,139,89,0.15);\n}\n\n.faq-question {\n  width: 100%;\n  padding: 18px 20px;\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 16px;\n  background: none;\n  border: none;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  text-align: left;\n  font-size: 15px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  color: #1A1A18;\n  transition: color 0.2s;\n}\n\n.faq-icon-wrap {\n  flex-shrink: 0;\n  width: 28px;\n  height: 28px;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  background: #F3E8D8;\n  border: 1px solid #E8D5BC;\n  display: grid;\n  place-items: center;\n  color: #B88B59;\n  transition: transform 0.3s, background 0.2s;\n}\n\n.faq-item.active .faq-icon-wrap {\n  transform: rotate(180deg);\n  background: #B88B59;\n  color: #fff;\n  border-color: #B88B59;\n}\n\n.faq-answer {\n  max-height: 0;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  transition: max-height 0.4s ease;\n}\n\n.faq-item.active .faq-answer {\n  max-height: 400px;\n}\n\n.faq-answer-content {\n  padding: 0 20px 18px;\n  border-top: 1px solid #F0E6D8;\n  margin: 0 20px;\n}\n\n.faq-answer-content p {\n  margin: 14px 0 0;\n  font-size: 14px;\n  line-height: 1.7;\n  color: #666;\n}\n\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n  .faq-section {\n    padding: 40px 12px;\n  }\n\n  .faq-title {\n    font-size: 24px;\n    margin-bottom: 28px;\n  }\n\n  .faq-question {\n    padding: 14px 16px;\n    font-size: 14px;\n  }\n\n  .faq-answer-content {\n    margin: 0 16px;\n    padding: 0 0 14px;\n  }\n\n  .faq-answer-content p {\n    font-size: 13px;\n  }\n}\n<\/style>\n\n<script>\n(function() {\n  var faqItems = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item');\n\n  faqItems.forEach(function(item) {\n    var question = item.querySelector('.faq-question');\n    var answer = item.querySelector('.faq-answer');\n\n    question.addEventListener('click', function() {\n      var isActive = item.classList.contains('active');\n\n      faqItems.forEach(function(other) {\n        if (other !== item) {\n          other.classList.remove('active');\n          other.querySelector('.faq-answer').style.maxHeight = null;\n          other.querySelector('.faq-question').setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');\n        }\n      });\n\n      if (isActive) {\n        item.classList.remove('active');\n        answer.style.maxHeight = null;\n        question.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');\n      } else {\n        item.classList.add('active');\n        answer.style.maxHeight = answer.scrollHeight + 'px';\n        question.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'true');\n      }\n    });\n  });\n})();\n<\/script>"}},"ss_simple_faq_pt7Ypk":{"type":"ss-simple-faq","blocks":{"text_g3KzEM":{"type":"text","settings":{"question":"La serrure est-elle compatible avec toutes les portes ?","answer":"<p>La serrure est conçue pour s’adapter à la majorité des portes standards. Son installation est simple et rapide, sans nécessiter de modifications importantes<\/p>"}},"text_wN8MmU":{"type":"text","settings":{"question":"Peut-on enregistrer plusieurs empreintes digitales ?","answer":"<p>Oui, il est possible d’enregistrer plusieurs empreintes digitales afin de permettre l’accès aux membres de votre famille ou aux personnes autorisées.<\/p>"}},"text_3aQqGp":{"type":"text","settings":{"question":"La serrure est-elle vraiment sécurisée ?","answer":"<p>Oui, la technologie de reconnaissance biométrique utilisée garantit un accès rapide et sécurisé, empêchant toute ouverture non autorisée.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["text_g3KzEM","text_wN8MmU","text_3aQqGp"],"disabled":true,"name":"Faq","settings":{"heading":"Questions Fréquentes","icon_color":"#ffffff","hover_color":"#efefef","question_color":"#ffffff","background_color":"#b88d5a","answer_color":"#000000","answer_bg_color":"#ffffff","questions-font-size":1.5}},"ss_text_block_cJtTTD":{"type":"ss-text-block","blocks":{"text_JxRgR3":{"type":"text","settings":{"heading":"<p>ZHANIMO<\/p>","color":"#d7a975","font_size":13,"richtext":"","richtext_color":"#ffd5a3","richtext_font_size":18}}},"block_order":["text_JxRgR3"],"name":"SS - Text block","settings":{"padding_header":0,"padding_button":0,"background-color":"#ffffff","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"section-width":80}},"newsletter_RmP4WW":{"type":"newsletter","blocks":{"heading_mpW9Eb":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"Rejoignez la communauté !","title_highlight_color":"#6d388b","heading_size":"h1"}},"paragraph_x68par":{"type":"paragraph","settings":{"text":"<p>Soyez le premier au courant de nos offres exclusives et nos surprises...<\/p>"}},"email_form_GMtNkM":{